Get Firmware for ESP32 from:

http://micropython.org/download

Erase flash:

~/Arduino/hardware/espressif/esp32/tools/esptool.py --port /dev/ttyUSB0 erase_flash

Flash Firware:

~/Arduino/hardware/espressif/esp32/tools/esptool.py --port /dev/ttyUSB0 --baud 460800 write_flash --flash_size=detect 0x1000 esp32-20181210-v1.9.4-740-gdc23978dd.bin

Test:

rshell --buffer-size=30 -p /dev/ttyUSB0


As well as the section "First micropython script" here:

https://diyprojects.io/unpacking-wemos-esp32-lolin32-lite-testing-firmware-micropython-raspberry-pi-3/#First_MicroPython_script


